Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.83,0:01:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,两次鼓动 兜的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.90,0:01:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.90,0:01:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你在虚张声势
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.70,0:01:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经…完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.10,0:02:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.60,0:02:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像这风中的残烛一般 颤抖不止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.50,0:02:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 兜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.20,0:02:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让她毫无痛苦地死去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.20,0:02:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…为了佐助 什么都能做的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以求你了 留下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很烦人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.50,0:03:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.90,0:03:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.10,0:03:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.10,0:03:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助…佐助在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.30,0:03:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的这副肉体就是佐助的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.50,0:03:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没必要再隐瞒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.70,0:03:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兜 你就告诉她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.90,0:03:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还是来晚了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.40,0:03:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸大人没能等到佐助的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.20,0:03:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经转生到别的容器里了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:03:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说佐助没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.10,0:04:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且就在这里的某处
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸大人为了等待下一次转生的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.50,0:04:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经给佐助下了咒印
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.50,0:04:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非所有的人都能承受这个咒印
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.70,0:04:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.90,0:04:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助没能承受住咒印 死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样 你撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定是在撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒谎对我而言 又有什么好处呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你反正…也快死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这么想见他 就成全你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:04:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你死了以后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.82,0:05:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就能在那个世界重逢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小樱 这种家伙说的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不能相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.58,0:05:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你早就死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一向言出必行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的忍道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在把佐助给带回来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是绝不会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:05:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小樱 你在这里躲一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影分身之术
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.20,0:06:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.89,0:06:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.40,0:06:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦无用光了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我痛快地揍你一顿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些烦人的分身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.10,0:07:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火遁.雾炎舞之术
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.20,0:07:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.60,0:07:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:08:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你和大蛇丸都在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.20,0:08:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 佐助也在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.70,0:08:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我说实话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么…回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体…动不了了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.80,0:08:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好看看自己的样子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.80,0:08:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是查克拉线啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.50,0:08:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查克拉…线…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.00,0:08:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在你刚才攻击的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.90,0:08:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把线缠到了你的身上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.80,0:08:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这线通向哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己好好看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.20,0:08:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.60,0:08:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条查克拉线
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.70,0:08:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与我心脏的经脉相通
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缠在你身上的线
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过你的经脉 内脏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你的心脏相连
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.50,0:09:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.50,0:09:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你的心脏…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久就会合二为一了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.30,0:09:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用查克拉凝结的线
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是绝对无法扯断的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.11,0:09:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的心脏已经完全同步了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我的心脏发出的查克拉线
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过经脉支配了你的心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.70,0:09:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 明明是我的心脏…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.00,0:09:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心跳加速的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心跳也会变快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心脏不再跳动时…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也会死去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.20,0:10:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止心脏跳动的话 你也会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这没什么不大了的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.50,0:10:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我的这副身体早已献给大蛇丸大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你要干吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.50,0:10:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我捏碎了这颗心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也会…死的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我捏碎了这颗心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.40,0:11:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也会…死的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.70,0:11:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 和我一起去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.10,0:11:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.70,0:11:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种心脏被握在手中的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻就会变得轻松起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你杀了我 鸣人也会死的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.20,0:11:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要砍的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.30,0:11:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用查克拉凝结的线
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.40,0:11:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不可能切断的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:12:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是纲手大人的怪力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.37,0:12:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也无法扯断它的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.90,0:12:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人就在我面前痛苦地挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.60,0:12:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我却什么忙也帮不上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.00,0:12:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…樱…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…绝对不会输的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.20,0:12:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我…完成自己的承诺之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逞强到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一块儿同归于尽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.50,0:12:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一块儿到佐助等候着我们的地方去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.90,0:13:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小樱姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莎美
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小樱姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.40,0:13:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这张符贴到苦无上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.30,0:13:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.60,0:13:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.40,0:13:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.65,0:13:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.50,0:13:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我的胸口跳得一塌糊涂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我白担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.44,0:14:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 小樱…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.80,0:14:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没辙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 莎莎美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.70,0:14:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏莎莎美救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.50,0:14:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.80,0:14:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的那个陷阱里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.80,0:14:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大水冲了进来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:14:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 这个陷阱的盖子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.50,0:15:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当水淹到天花板的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拼命想打开陷阱的盖子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无奈纹丝不动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.50,0:15:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然自来也大人要我到半崎那儿去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我怎么也放心不下岚哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.90,0:15:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑过来一看…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.60,0:15:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛤蟆说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:15:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过现在想想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我怎么推
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不可能打开盖子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.30,0:16:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.60,0:16:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.24,0:16:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么用苦无无法切断的线
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贴上了莎莎美的符后就切断了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.30,0:16:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查克拉线
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们风马忍法奥义中的奥义
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.30,0:16:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风马的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.20,0:16:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙又是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…是刚才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.80,0:16:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜉蝣大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.80,0:16:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是风马的上忍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莎美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莎美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:17:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸大人复活了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 被大蛇丸给骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.70,0:17:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.30,0:17:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岚呢 莎莎美的表哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.70,0:17:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他现在人在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.60,0:17:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我们风马一族…拉上了忍者的正面舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.40,0:17:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还这么说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.10,0:17:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少把真相告诉莎莎美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在那里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莎美和岚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.31,0:17:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人以前的关系可好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 相见不如怀念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.80,0:18:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜉蝣大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莎美 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里等我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.70,0:18:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去见他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管那里有什么在等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.30,0:18:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了见岚哥哥才来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有勇气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.70,0:18:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那就一起过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莎美…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.10,0:19:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许里边会有什么机关
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.20,0:19:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.90,0:19:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.00,0:19:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得正好 莎莎美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.80,0:19:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岚哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:19:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岚哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.80,0:20:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是岚了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.80,0:20:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这究竟…是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.20,0:20:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用风马上忍的忍术把肉体融合了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.60,0:20:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成了最强的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.50,0:20:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.90,0:20:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让你见识一下我最强的忍术吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.40,0:20:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莎美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.70,0:20:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样 岚哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸那个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝饶不了他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.10,0:22:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.30,0:22:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.00,0:22:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果我还是什么都没做到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.00,0:22:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是拖你的后腿 毫无改变
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.40,0:22:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是鸣人 莎莎美
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.70,0:22:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们教会了我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.00,0:22:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想改变一下自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.10,0:22:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.40,0:23:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一次轮到我来努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.10,0:23:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.04,0:23:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小樱的决心